FBIS3-42310 "jptot007__l94096" JPRS-TOT-94-007-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 16 February 1994 CENTRAL EURASIA ARMENIA Youth Group Threatens Terrorism If Aliyev Does Not Resign NC0702205394 Yerevan SNARK in English 1244 GMT 7 Feb 94 NC0702205394 Yerevan SNARK Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Baku, Feb 7, (SNARK) -- Confidential sources in Baku told SNARK that the youth patriotic organization entering the Azerbaijani People's Front has appealed Geydar Aliyev to resign as a president. Otherwise, the organization threatens to effect terrorist and sabotage acts on Azerbaijan territory. In this connection, the official circles in Azerbaijan do not rule out that the recent explosion in the Baku-Kislovodsk passenger train was undertaken by fighters of this organization.
